Trademark Attribution and Fair Use Notice
================================================================================

Holo-VTL is a virtual tape library that emulates SCSI device identities of real
tape and library hardware so that backup software which whitelists specific
vendor / product / firmware combinations can interoperate with virtual devices.
The emulated identifiers (Vendor IDentification, Product IDentification, VPD
pages, density codes, element addresses, mode pages) are derived from public
SCSI specifications (SPC-4, SSC-3, SMC-3) and from vendor-published device
documentation.

