================================================================================
Provenance Statement
================================================================================

Holo-VTL is an independent, clean-room implementation. It contains no source
code derived from mhvtl, quadstorvtl, or any other GPL/AGPL/LGPL-licensed
virtual-tape-library project. Naming patterns such as "drive_type_v*" and
"library_type_v*" exist only as configuration aliases to ease migration from
deployments that previously used those identifiers; they are not derived code
or copied artifacts.

Every emulated SCSI command path, mode page, log page, and element-address
layout is built from publicly available specifications (T10 documents) and
vendor-published manuals. Where vendor-specific behavior is required for
interoperability, the implementation derives the behavior from observation of
the public spec, not from any proprietary source.

